<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_261_r1l4"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Markhart VValtmans </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r1l5"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> wie ew </del> vnd <expan>beſund<ex>er</ex></expan> wie er ew <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r1l6">in gaſtes vveıſe mit <expan>fürſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cʒü <expan>geſproch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab / . Laſſen wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r1l7">ewr erberkeit vviſſen / daʒ wir Jm mit ew cʒerechten nicht <expan>empfolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r1l11"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jn auch 
<add><ab facs="#facs_261_line_1576580388775_2595">auf <expan>dıſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cʒeite </ab></add> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> vnſerſelbs <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> nicht hinab geſchıcket </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r1l12"><expan>Dan<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ wir Jn dem Jacob Topler <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> gelıhen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r1l13">vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jm vnſer betbrief <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gnedıgen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r1l16"><expan>wircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> / . Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_261_line_1576580403481_2611">diener </ab></add> darvmb auch cʒerede </ab>
