</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_261" id="130r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Balthasar <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Maspach,
                                <expan>tümh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czü
                            <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> und probst czü Onelspach </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Markhart Waltmans,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>besund<ex>er</ex></expan>, wie er ew
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> in gastes weise mit
                            <expan>fürsprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czü
                            <expan>gesproch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab; lassen wir ewr erberkeit wissen,
                        daz wir im mit ew cze rechten nicht <expan>empfolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> in auch
                            <add>auf <expan>diselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czeite
                                </add><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> unserselbs
                            <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> nicht hinab geschicket,
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> daz wir in dem Jacob Topler,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> gelihen
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> im
                        unser betbrief <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> an
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gnedigen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>. Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir den
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<add>diener</add> darumb auch czerede gesaczt und in
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief lassen hören und der hat uns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, wie ir der sache gen Jacoben
                        Topler für ewch <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> und der Markhart von
                                <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jacob
                            <expan>Topl<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>belib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> seit, und <expan>gegange<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hint<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gnedigen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>, des er sich an
                            <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> gnad cziehe. Und dem sey er
                                <expan>nachgange<ex>n</ex></expan> und hab ew
                                    <add><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> sein selbs
                                    <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan></add> darumb czügesprochen, als im
                        danyden geraten sey worden, und hab ew <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> nicht
                                <expan>czügesproch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und wir
                            <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ewr erberkeit
                                <expan>fleizziklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz ir das gen dem
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> Jacob Toppler
                                <expan>gelimppflich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> für ew nemen und ew des
                                <expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>czerynne<ex>n</ex></expan> lassen wöllet, also daz derselb
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> unser
                            <expan>darynne<ex>n</ex></expan> geniesze. Das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
